rows.label: tlk000004_msg0001
rows.name:
Just letting you know, it's a good way
to Fons Maim from here.

rows.label: tlk000004_msg0005
rows.name:
Take your time. Just gimme a shout
whenever you're ready.

rows.label: tlk000004_msg0006
rows.name:
Plenty of monsters out there on the
road. Make sure you've got yourselves
all kitted up before we head out.

rows.label: tlk000004_msg0007
rows.name:
All set? Then let's get our backsides
over to Fons Maim, pronto!
